@arcaneimperator  

You can pay extort on the third [Knight of Infamy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Knight of Infamy) up to three times for 1 mana each- each opponent loses 1 life and you gain 1\*(number of opponents) life for each time you extort.  

The third Knight can't extort itself because at the time you cast it it's a spell and not a creature. It only has Extort once it's resolved and entered the battlefield.
